   <varlistentry xml:id="vle.ha.docupdates.sle12_ga.basics">
    <term><xref linkend="cha.ha.config.basics"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="sec.ha.config.basics.global.stonith"/> mentions
        policy change in DLM services when the global cluster option
        <literal>stonith-enabled</literal> is set to
        <literal>false</literal> (Fate#315195).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="sec.ha.config.basics.tags"/> describes a new option
        to group conceptually related resources, without creating any
        colocation or ordering relationship between them (Fate#315101).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="sec.ha.config.basics.constraints.rscset"/> explains
        the concept of resource sets as an alternative format for defining
        constraints. As of &productname; 12, resource sets can now also
        be used within location constraints (whereas they could formerly
        only be used within colocation and ordering constraints).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Restructured <xref linkend="sec.ha.config.basics.maint.mode"/> to
        also cover the option of setting a whole cluster to maintenance mode
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=829864"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added attributes for <literal>pacemaker_remote</literal> service to
        <xref linkend="tab.ha.basics.meta"/> and added new section:
        <xref linkend="sec.ha.config.basics.remote"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=853535"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added new resource agent classes to
        <xref linkend="sec.ha.config.basics.raclasses"/>:
        <literal>systemd</literal>, <literal>service</literal>, and
        <literal>nagios</literal>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=853520"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated <xref linkend="sec.ha.config.basics.remote.nagios"/> to
        reflect the package name changes from
        <systemitem>nagios-plugins</systemitem> and
        <systemitem>nagios-plugins-metadata</systemitem> to
        <systemitem>monitoring-plugins</systemitem> and
        <systemitem>monitoring-plugins-metadata</systemitem>, respectively
        (Fate#317780).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
